| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0459 — Recovery Inhibition (titan)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 8450ccc3-bef8-5ce6-a7db-4a9e8a415f5b"
